structure.unit: FEES AND COMPENSATION OF PUBLIC OFFICERS AND EMPLOYEES

law.history: Repealed 1962 Ky. Acts ch. 145, sec. 1. -- Amended 1956 Ky. Acts ch. 238, sec. 1. -- Created 1950 Ky. Acts ch. 123, sec. 16.
